name: LASTMILE_PROBE_RESULT_STATE
description: The status of the last-mile network tests.

parameters.LASTMILE_PROBE_RESULT_COMPLETE: 1: The last-mile network probe test is complete.

parameters.LASTMILE_PROBE_RESULT_INCOMPLETE_NO_BWE: 2: The last-mile network probe test is incomplete because the bandwidth estimation is not available due to limited test resources.

parameters.LASTMILE_PROBE_RESULT_UNAVAILABLE: 3: The last-mile network probe test is not carried out, probably due to poor network conditions.
